### b) Recovery Timing Monitoring

Monitoring was not added as a formal metric + threshold, and instead assessed for reasonableness.

It was noted that:

* 63.8% of recoveries (count-based) occur within 8 quarters of default; and
* 77.6% of recovery balances occur within 8 quarters of default.

The original question was whether 8 quarters is appropriate for the recovery timing assumption.

